        <date when="1396-08-17">1396 August 17</date>
      </creation></profileDesc></teiHeader><text><body><div type="header"><p>Verwandtschajtsweisung für Anna, Gattin des Konrad Ganyczer</p></div><div><p> Einbr. 2 Zg. (Indez: Item freuntschaft Annen Chunrats hausfraw des Ganiczer) <rs type="event" ref="ev__StB_I_73">Des nagsten phincztags vor sand Pertelmes tag kom fur
            den rat der stat ze Wienn <rs type="fn" role="other"><rs type="person" ref="pe__anna_StB_I_73"><roleName type="title">fraw</roleName> Ann, <roleName type="kin" corresp="pe__konrad_ganiczer_StB_I_73"><add>hawsfraw</add></roleName>
                <roleName type="kin" corresp="pe__bernhard_wechsl_von_hainfeld_StB_I_73"><add>rechtew swester
                    tochter</add></roleName>
                <roleName type="kin" corresp="pe__margarethe_StB_I_73"><add>rechtew swester
                    tochter</add></roleName>
                <rs type="person" ref="pe__konrad_ganiczer_StB_I_73">Chunrats hawsfraw des
                  Ganyczer</rs></rs>, und <triggerstring n="fn">hat da beweist</triggerstring></rs>
            <rs type="fn" role="witness">mit den erbern leuten, mit <rs type="person" ref="pe__niklas_radschmied_QGW_II_I_1062"><roleName type="title"><add>erbern
                    leuten</add></roleName> Niclasen <roleName type="prof" cert="unknown">dem
                  Radsmyd</roleName>, <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien">die zeit des
                  rats der stat ze Wienn</roleName></rs>, und mit <rs type="person" ref="pe__otto_radschmied_StB_I_73"><roleName type="title"><add>erbern
                  leuten</add></roleName>Otten <roleName type="prof" cert="unknown">dem
                  Radsmyd</roleName></rs></rs>, das <rs type="fn" role="recipient"><rs type="person" ref="pe__anna_StB_I_73">sy</rs></rs>
            <rs type="fn" role="issuer"><rs type="person" ref="pe__bernhard_wechsl_von_hainfeld_StB_I_73">Wernharts des Wechsleins von Haymfeld, <roleName type="dead">dem got
                  genad</roleName></rs>, rechtew swester tochter gewesen ist, <rs type="person" ref="pe__margarethe_StB_I_73"><roleName type="title">frawn </roleName>Margretn,
                weylnt <roleName type="kin" corresp="pe__bernhard_wechsl_von_hainfeld_StB_I_73"><add>rechtew
                    swester</add></roleName><rs type="person" ref="pe__thomas_apotheker_StB_I_73">Thommans des Apoteker <roleName type="dead"><add>den auch bayden got
                    genad</add></roleName></rs>
                <roleName type="kin" corresp="pe__thomas_apotheker_StB_I_73">hawsfrawn</roleName>,
                  <roleName type="dead">den auch bayden got genad</roleName></rs></rs>. Als darumb
            die obgenanten erbern leut mit irn trewn an ayde stat vor offem rat habent gesagt, als
            sy ze recht solten.</rs>
        </p></div><div type="lists"><xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../indices/placeList.xml" xpointer="element(/1/2/1/1)"/><xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../indices/personList.xml" xpointer="element(/1/2/1/1)"/><xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../indices/eventList.xml" xpointer="element(/1/2/1/1)"/><xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../indices/orgList.xml" xpointer="element(/1/2/1/1)"/></div></body></text></TEI>